{{italic title}}
'''''Barsa''''' is a famous [[encyclopedia]] from [[Latin America]]. It is widely known in [[Brazil]], [[Argentina]], [[Chile]], [[Venezuela]] and [[Mexico]]. It has [[printed]] versions in [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]] and [[Spanish language|Spanish]] with nine volumes each and 2,842 pages. Barsa also has a [[multimedia]] version.

