{{primary sources|date=July 2012}}
The '''Honduras Top 50''' is the official airplay [[music chart]] in Honduras. Chart rankings are based on radio play and surveyed through radio stations in San Pedro Sula, Tegucigalpa, La Ceiba, Puerto Cortés, Choluteca and Roaton.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tiempo.hn/fuzion/top-50|title=Top 50|work=Fuzion|publisher=El Tiempo |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120909094233/http://tiempo.hn/fuzion/top-50 |archivedate=2012-09-09 |accessdate=2013-09-13}}</ref> The charts are compiled by ''Fuzion'' magazine and published by [[El Tiempo (Honduras)|''El Tiempo'']].

