{{Use Irish English|date=May 2017}}
'''[[Margaret Gallagher]]''' is an Irish<ref name=Global>{{cite web | title = Margaret Gallagher| url = http://www.globalmediapolicy.net/node/1112 | website = globalmediapolicy.net | publisher = Mapping Global Media Policy | access-date = 19 October 2015 }}</ref> freelance researcher and writer specialising in gender and media. She has carried out research, development and evaluation projects for the [[United Nations Statistics Division]], [[United Nations Development Fund for Women|UNIFEM]], [[UNESCO]], the [[International Labour Organization|International Labour Office]], the [[Council of Europe]], the [[European Commission]] and the [[European Audiovisual Observatory]].<ref name=SMTYEWTK>{{cite web | title = "SMTYEWTK (Still... More Than You Ever Wanted to Know) About Women in Journalism and Mass Communications" Research Group: Bios: Margaret Gallagher | url = http://www.uky.edu/~clevitt/rrrush/rrrush/GallaherBio.htm | website = uky.edu | publisher = [[University of Kentucky]] | access-date = 19 October 2015 }}</ref>

